  "summary": "## Summary: Add useMemo for expensive in-render computations\n\n### Changes Implemented\n- **Dashboard.tsx**: Added `useMemo` for:\n  - `StatCards`: `durationLabel` and `wpmLabel` computations\n  - `LanguagePie`: `total` (reduce) and `chartData` (map) computations\n  - `CorrectionFrequency`: `maxCount` (Math.max with spread) and `chartData` (slice+map)\n  - `TopModels`: `maxSessions` (Math.max with spread)\n  - `FillerStatsChart`: `maxCount` (Math.max with spread)\n  - All with performance budget comments (`< 0.1ms` to `< 0.5ms`)\n\n- **History.tsx**: Added `useMemo` for:\n  - `SessionRow`: `preview` string slice computation\n  - `SessionDrawer`: `installedModels` filter computation\n  - All with performance budget comments\n\n- **Models.tsx**: Added `useMemo` for:\n  - `defaultsByLang` lookup map construction\n  - `visible` filtered and sorted model list\n  - `DefaultSelector`: `installed` filter\n  - All with performance budget comments (`< 0.2ms` to `< 1ms`)\n\n- **Pill.tsx**: Added `useMemo` for:\n  - `IdleContent`: `wordCount` computation\n  - `SuccessContent`: `preview` string slice\n  - All with performance budget comments (`< 0.1ms`)\n\n- **ExpandedPill.tsx**: Added `useMemo` for:\n  - `wordCount` split+filter computation\n  - With performance budget comment\n\n- **Dictionary.tsx**: Added `useMemo` for:\n  - `FillerWordsTab`: `filtered` language filter\n  - With performance budget comment (`< 0.2ms`)\n\n### Files Modified\n- `src/pages/Dashboard.tsx`\n- `src/pages/History.tsx`\n- `src/pages/Models.tsx`\n- `src/pages/Dictionary.tsx`\n- `src/components/pill/Pill.tsx`\n- `src/components/pill/ExpandedPill.tsx`\n\n### Notes for Developer\n- All `useMemo` hooks include performance budget comments (e.g., `// < 0.5ms`) to flag future regressions\n- Precise dependency arrays ensure re-computation only when necessary\n- Build verified successfully with `npm run build`\n- TypeScript compilation passed with no errors"
